---
import settings from '../data/settings.json';
---
// About.astro
---
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <div class="about-visual fade-in">
      <div class="about-img-wrap">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520854221256-17451cc331bf?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" 
          alt="Trabajando en detalle decorativo" 
          class="about-img"
        />
        <div class="floating-badge float-anim" style="animation-duration: 5s">
          <span class="badge-num">100%</span>
          <span class="badge-text">Personalizado</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-text-content fade-in d-2">
        <p class="section-label">Sobre Nosotros</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">{settings.aboutTitle}</h2>
        <p class="about-desc">
          {settings.aboutText}
        </p>
        <p>
          Cada proyecto es trabajado con máxima dedicación, combinando técnicas artesanales con 
          materiales modernos como resina y styrofoam de alta densidad. Creemos que la belleza 
          está en los detalles y que cada evento merece una decoración verdaderamente única.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <ul class="about-features">
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="check-icon">
            <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Materiales premium y acabados duraderos
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="check-icon">
            <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Diseños adaptados a tu visión y temática
        </li>
        <li>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="check-icon">
            <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          Puntualidad y atención constante al detalle
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 5rem;
  align-items: center;
}

/* -- Visual Side -- */
.about-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  padding-right: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
}

.about-img-wrap::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 2rem;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  z-index: -1;
}

.about-img {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.floating-badge {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 4rem;
  left: -2rem;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-dark);
}
.badge-num {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: var(--size-2xl);
  color: var(--color-accent-dark);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.badge-text {
  font-size: var(--size-xs);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-text);
}

/* -- Content Side -- */
.about-text {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.about-features {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.about-features li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
  color: var(--color-heading);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.check-icon {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  color: var(--color-accent-dark);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .about-visual {
    order: 2;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-content {
    order: 1;
  }
}
</style>
